xt-foreground-muted\">Your Name</label><input type=\"text\" required=\"\" placeholder=\"Marcus Vance\" class=\"w-full bg-background border border-border rounded-xl px-4 py-2.5 text-xs text-foreground focus:outline-none focus:border-primary transition font-medium\" value=\"\"/></div><div class=\"space-y-1.5\"><label class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-foreground-muted\">Email Address</label><input type=\"email\" required=\"\" placeholder=\"you@example.com\" class=\"w-full bg-background border border-border rounded-xl px-4 py-2.5 text-xs text-foreground focus:outline-none focus:border-primary transition font-medium\" value=\"\"/></div></div><div class=\"space-y-1.5\"><label class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-foreground-muted\">Subject / Department</label><select class=\"w-full bg-background border border-border rounded-xl px-4 py-2.5 text-xs text-foreground focus:outline-none focus:border-primary transition font-medium\"><option value=\"General\" selected=\"\">General Support</option><option value=\"Calibration\">Telemetry &amp; Calibration Feedback</option><option value=\"Guides\">DIY Repair Guides Feedback</option><option value=\"Business\">Business Inquiries</option></select></div><div class=\"space-y-1.5\"><label class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-foreground-muted\">Your Message</label><textarea rows=\"5\" required=\"\" placeholder=\"Enter the details of your inquiry, including gamepad model if relevant...\" class=\"w-full bg-background border border-border rounded-xl px-4 py-2.5 text-xs text-foreground focus:outline-none focus:border-primary transition font-medium leading-relaxed resize-none\"></textarea></div><button type=\"submit\" class=\"w-full py-3 bg-primary hover:bg-primary-hover border border-primary-hover text-xs font-bold text-white rounded-xl shadow-lg shadow-primary/10 transition-all duration-300 flex items-center justify-center gap-2\">Send Message</button></form></div><div class=\"md:col-span-2 space-y-6\"><div class=\"bg-surface/50 border border-border rounded-3xl p-6 shadow-xl backdrop-blur-md space-y-4\"><h3 class=\"text-sm font-black text-foreground uppercase tracking-wider\">Direct Contacts</h3><div class=\"space-y-3.5 text-xs\"><div><span class=\"text-foreground-muted block text-[10px] font-bold uppercase\">Founder &amp; Workshop Tech</span><a href=\"mailto:marcus.vance@gamepadtester.live\" class=\"text-primary hover:underline font-mono text-[11px]\">marcus.vance@gamepadtester.live</a></div><div><span class=\"text-foreground-muted block text-[10px] font-bold uppercase\">Systems &amp; Latency Consultant</span><a href=\"mailto:sarah.chen@gamepadtester.live\" class=\"text-success hover:underline font-mono text-[11px]\">sarah.chen@gamepadtester.live</a></div><div><span class=\"text-foreground-muted block text-[10px] font-bold uppercase\">Firmware &amp; QA Telemetry</span><a href=\"mailto:alex.mercer@gamepadtester.live\" class=\"text-warning hover:underline font-mono text-[11px]\">alex.mercer@gamepadtester.live</a></div><div><span class=\"text-foreground-muted block text-[10px] font-bold uppercase\">General Inquiries</span><a href=\"mailto:support@gamepadtester.live\" class=\"text-foreground hover:underline font-mono text-[11px]\">support@gamepadtester.live</a></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-surface/50 border border-border rounded-3xl p-6 shadow-xl backdrop-blur-md space-y-2.5\"><h3 class=\"text-sm font-black text-foreground uppercase tracking-wider\">Lab Location</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-foreground-secondary leading-relaxed\">GamepadTester Hardware Lab<br/>404 Calibration Way, Suite 100<br/>San Francisco, CA 94107</p><div class=\"text-[10px] text-foreground-muted\">Note: Our physical lab is dedicated to testing bench research and not open to unscheduled repair drop-offs. Please contact us via email first.</div></div></div></div></div></div><footer class=\"bg-surface border-t border-border py-12\"><div class=\"container-custom\"><d